---
import { company, consultHref } from '../data/site';
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 md:px-8">
    <div
      class="reveal relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl px-6 py-14 md:px-16 md:py-20 text-center"
      style="background-color: var(--navy); color: #ffffff;"
    >
      <!-- 装飾（オレンジのグロー） -->
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(70% 120% at 100% 0%, rgba(233,120,28,0.35), transparent 55%), radial-gradient(60% 120% at 0% 100%, rgba(233,120,28,0.18), transparent 55%);"
      >
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <h2 class="heading" style="color:#ffffff; font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);">
          住まいのこと、まずはお気軽にご相談を
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl mx-auto text-base md:text-lg" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);">
          ご相談は無料です。売却・購入・リフォーム・住宅ローンまで、専門スタッフが丁寧にお応えします。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href={consultHref}
            class="w-full sm:w-auto rounded-full px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
            style="background-color: var(--accent); color: #ffffff;"
          >
            無料相談・お問い合わせ
          </a>
          <a
            href={company.telHref}
            class="w-full sm:w-auto rounded-full px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold border-2 transition-transform hover:-translate-y-0.5"
            style="border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); color: #ffffff;"
          >
            お電話：{company.tel}
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
